brandDetail.brandDetail: Xiaomi Mobile, MIUI, Mi Chat, Xiaomi Net, Xiaomi Box, Xiaomi TV and Xiaomi Router are the seven core businesses of Xiaomi Company. ""Being born with a fever"" is the product philosophy of Xiaomi. Xiaomi Company pioneered the development of a mobile operating system model using the Internet model, making Xiaomi mobile phone the world's first Internet mobile phone brand. And develop, market and sell Xiaomi's products through the Internet.
